The '''International Folklore Children’s Festival "Oro Bez Granici"''' ({{lang-mk|Интернационален фолклорен детски фестивал "Оро Без Граници"}}, ''Internacionalen folkloren detski festival "Oro Bez Granici"'') is a festival taking place every year between 29 September and 2 October in the Universal Hall in [[Skopje]], [[Republic of Macedonia]]. In this festival, children’s [[folklore]] ensembles from Macedonia and abroad participate.

